name: Siaki Tuikabe
story: Siaki Tuikabe grew up in the Caribbean and joined the BLUFOR military at a young age. He quickly moved up the ranks due to his natural leadership skills and dedication to the cause. After several years of service, Siaki decided to transition into law enforcement as a way to continue serving his community. He takes pride in his work as a police officer and strives to maintain peace and order in his district.
